      <div>
        <span class="target">Target</span>
        <h4 class="goal-title">
            <div class="field field--name-name field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">2.b</div>
      </h4>
        <p class="goal-text">Correct and prevent trade restrictions and distortions in world agricultural markets, including through the parallel elimination of all forms of agricultural export subsidies and all export measures with equivalent effect, in accordance with the mandate of the Doha Development Round</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="indicators">
    <div class="indicators-header">
